Package: otargen
Type: Package
Title: R package to access Open Target Genetics
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Amir", "Feizi", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "afeizi@gmail.com"),
    person("Kamalika", "Ray", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Amir Feizi <afeizi@gmail.com>
Description: This R package provides functionalities to search and retrieve data tables from Open Target Genetics using GraphQL queries. It offers an interface to interact with the Open Target Genetics GraphQL endpoints, making it easier to access and analyze genetic data.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
